    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a full, honest picture so you can shop with confidence. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 you'll notice only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use, with no significant dents or rust. The paint retains good color and gloss. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-maintained; the upholstery shows modest wear but no tears or major staining, and all controls and features function as intended. Mechanically, this car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, shifts are clean, and the brakes respond well. It's not a showroom-fresh vehicle, but it's genuinely solid and ready for everyday driving without any known issues requiring immediate attention. A great choice for a buyer looking for dependable transportation at a fair price.",
      "price": 32000.0,
