      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid Everyday Driver at an Honest Fair-Condition Price! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag? This vehicle is a practical choice for budget-conscious buyers who want something that gets the job done. It shows the expected wear and imperfections of a well-used car \u2014 it's not perfect, but it runs and drives, making it a great candidate for someone who needs reliable daily transport. Priced fairly to reflect its condition, this is a straightforward, no-surprises deal for the right buyer. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present one of the finest examples you'll find on the market today. The exterior is absolutely stunning \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of scratches, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, all trim pieces are intact and gleaming, and the glass is crystal clear with no chips or cracks. The interior is equally impressive: the seats, dashboard, and door panels show no signs of wear, fading, or damage, and everything smells fresh and clean. All electronics, controls, and comfort features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, dry, and well-maintained, with no leaks or unusual noises. The mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and drivetrain \u2014 all perform flawlessly. Service records are available and reflect consistent, proper maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. If you're looking for a car you can drive with complete confidence from day one, this is it.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, making it a dependable and practical choice for buyers seeking reliable used transportation. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor cosmetic wear such as light surface scratches and small scuffs consistent with normal everyday use \u2014 nothing that detracts significantly from its appearance. The paint retains good color and shine, and the body panels are straight with no major dents or structural concerns. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; upholstery shows moderate use with minor wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but there are no tears or significant staining. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are in good working order, and the car starts reliably and drives smoothly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been maintained adequately and should provide continued dependable service with routine upkeep. Buyers can expect a solid, honest used car that performs well day-to-day without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle.",
